  <summary date="2022-07-22T15:22:10Z" status="Introduced in House">Healthy Future Students and Earth Pilot Program Act of 2021

This bill establishes a pilot program for providing 100% plant-based food and milk options in school meals.

The Department of Agriculture must award up to 50 grants to school food authorities. Recipients may use funds for activities including training food service personnel on serving 100% plant-based options and covering additional costs of buying plant-based foods and milks.</summary>
